// SagaPatternType: ORCHESTRATION | CHOREOGRAPHY
// SagaWorkflowType: ISSUE_TO_EXECUTION | EXECUTION_TO_PR | PR_TO_MERGE | FULL_ISSUE_LIFECYCLE | WORKTREE_SETUP | CUSTOM
